title: 【#スバおか】マリオテニスフィーバーで遊ぶしゅばあああああああああああああああああ！！！：Mario Tennis Fever【ホロライブ/大空スバル】
name: Oozora Subaru

entries.text: By the way, is the audio okay?
Is the sound popping at all?
Did you just wake up? Correct, correct, correct. Hello, Just-Woke-Up.
Okay, so! Also, Nekomata-san is actually just a static PNG today, but please treat her well.
Yeah, time has stopped for me. My time is frozen. So we can do whatever we want.
Our beginnings always start with tennis.
Yeah, that's true. We have a long history.
Yeah, SubaOka actually started by staying up all night watching Prince of Tennis, so our tennis history is deep.
Well, well, well. So today we're going to play some proper tennis. Are you ready?
Yes, yes, of course. You could say this is the ancestor of the SubaOka Party.
Well, that's true. While eating pickles.
I want to play while remembering those days we spent staying up all night watching Prince of Tennis and eating pickles.
Right, along with some slightly fancy bottled apple juice.
Woah. Wait, wasn't it grape juice?
Ah, Welch's. The days of drinking Welch's and eating pickles.
Okay, okay, okay. Closing entries, closing entries.
By the way, I heard there are a lot of characters.
Nekomata-san, you've played this once before, right?
Yeah, first of all... I've only played it once.
Subaru just started earlier, so I don't have any characters.
I only have about 3 extra ones myself.
For me, Power type is the only choice.
Then Subaru will go with the All-Rounder Daisy.
Is it tee-tee? It's tee-tee, right?
I don't know, I just booted it up and I had this racket.
Then Subaru will use the muddy racket.
I don't even know what effect this special racket has.
You're just someone who wants to harvest bananas!
Your harvesting power is too strong!
Also, I forgot to turn off the Flower!
Like, I forgot to turn off the commentary flower!
Yeah, this guy talks so much!
Looks like you ate too much.
Don't score with a body shot!
Does returning a shot in the mud reduce HP?
This IS tennis! If I say it's tennis!
Look, the feet are so fast.
I'll shake you left and right!
That clumsy movement just now was crazy.
I couldn't use the Fever Shot well!
The bananas are scattered, it's a greengrocer!
It goes down when you take a special move, when you fall...
And when you get hit in the face with the ball.
No, no, losing HP in tennis? What is that?
Well, true. That means this isn't normal tennis. Basically.
Exactly. This one is open. Waluigi Pinball Stage.
There shouldn't be any gimmicks I think.
Nice. Since I unlocked stuff, I'll try someone else.
Koro-san used that before and said it was hard.
He is Power type after all.
This tornado is dangerous! The tornado!
The tornado is raging too much!
Seriously, the wind is too annoying.
No, no! Don't draw pictures! Pictures!
I can't see the screen anymore!
I can't see the screen, it's brutal!
It's a total mess, it's brutal!
Is it like Blooper in Mario Kart?
Come on, come on, come on.
True, this isn't just TV! It's a battle!!
Ah, this is bad, this no—
If you try to avoid the mud...
You have no choice but to enter the mud!
No! I don't want to go in the mud! Your HP is getting shaved way too much!
Wait, is it the mud's fault?
What is that fake Echizen Ryoma vibe? Not yet, not yet!
I'll run even through the mud!
You still have a ways to go.
An elementary schooler pretending to be Echizen.
I didn't even notice the flower talking.
I want to use someone cute.
They say it's a Rosetta (Rosalina) meta.
I don't think it dirties the stage or anything.
I'll go with the Electric Racket.
You are going to become a mother!
Eh? Why say that? Wait, it's floating, that's crazy!
Wait a second, the floating is crazy!
So the ball curves a lot.
It returns to the center when you hit it.
Shut up!! I know that much!
The ball returns to the center!
Subaru-chan's probably curves that much too.
Sending it to the middle is nasty.
Subaru-chan's probably curves too, I think.
Look, look! Curve left, curve right!
No time to even unleash my electric shock?!
You're right. No good, if it curves, the character just...
If I don't graduate from button mashing, I can't win this.
When you graduate from button mashing, Subaru-chan wins.
I will graduate from button mashing!
Want to try the same racket?
Stop it, stop it! That will just expose how bad I am!
I'm using a racket Subaru-chan doesn't have.
Eh, what is that? It's super nice.
If you play a bit, the rackets appear.
Who should I pick... I'll pick this one.
Kamek made me suffer earlier, so I have memories.
Ah, right, you're playing it. Mario World.
You were talking about Kesaran Pasaran or something.
Oh right, I thought it was a Kesaran Pasaran...
But apparently it wasn't a Kesaran Pasaran.
It was a Tumbleweed, that story.
No, no, she's a grandma, seriously.
There's two of them! There's two of them!
It was too fast, there were two of them left.
Where should I stand?! My HP is bad!
I'm gonna die! I'm gonna die!
Please! The other me! Do it!
Wow, there's a Biri-Q here too.
No no, why do you sound happy?
What! Woah! I'm the idiot chasing the ball into the opponent's court!
Just now, the ball my ally hit somehow hit me...
Something is going 'thump thump', it's scary, what is this?
That's not heart failure, it's match point.
Not bad, this game is interesting!
Give me that electric ball thing too.
I want to, I want to, I want to.
Getting hit by my ally's ball is a mystery.
It IS tennis. This proves that the tennis we love was always like this.
Well, true, the tennis we love was always like this.
This is a Special Game Match.
I've never done it. What is that?
Nekomata-san, you're really good at Mario Tennis.
I don't really feel confident though.
What kind of match is the next one?
Is there anything more chaotic than what we just did?
Look, just because you add Fever...
Doesn't mean you can do whatever you want!
Start from the top. Ring Shot.
Apparently you feed balls to the Piranha Plant on the opponent's court.
I don't get it. I don't get it at all.
I can change Koopa Troopa's color, but seeing is believing.
Eh? Is there a Piranha Plant?
I can't return to my turtle form.
No, I'm a turtle, but I'm stuck in the shell state and can't go back.
Ah, the filling won't come out?
Right, right, the filling won't come out. Right.
Maybe if you stop, it'll come out?
This is a bit of a high-level character.
Crap, only my court is getting wider.
Isn't it better if it's wider?
True. But if it's wide, the area I have to cover increases.
Isn't it like... if it gets wide, do you die instantly?
But if it turns green, it's instant death.
Is the turtle just hard in the first place?
Anywhere is tax-free! But I have Fever too, so I have to Fever.
Maybe Koopa Troopa was too hard.
In this game, the one with the bigger build wins.
So much stuff, what is this?
Look at it for a sec.
I was sightseeing and I scored.
What is this? What is this?
I think if you hit the round things with the ball...
If you hit this round thing with the ball, it goes *gon gon gon gon*.
I can't control it that well though.
Ah, it became your ball... crap, there are two balls!
Bad bad bad bad bad bad.
Ah, a hand is coming in.
Umm, if you do Fever 3 times, the person who put it in the 3rd time starts the pinball.
Ah, I see... I don't know! Why does Pinball start?!
That's the kind of stage it is. Look, it says Waluigi Pinball.
Ah, true. It was Waluigi Pinball. I see.
There's a lot. Let's try Ring Shot too.
Seriously, I got stuck and couldn't get out, thought it was over.
This has been around for a while, since the N64 days.
Crap, I think I'm good at this.
Balls coming from the side is brutal.
"If you hit the lit-up floor panels on the opponent's court, you get one Fever Shot."
I see, control seems important again.
It's technique after all. I'll go with Peach.
It's always Peach in any era.
Peach-san is always doing her best.
It stops being a normal racket, surely.
I think you just shoot a special move like always.
Go ahead and beat me up.
Quickly, let me use Donkey Kong!
It's a game of strength! I want to do that too!
That's where the talking Flower is from.
There are seeds in the bottom left and right...
I really want Subaru-chan to play Wonder.
I played Wonder once with Calliope.
Back then I didn't play action games yet.
If you win, you get it.
I think if you collect them all...
You can go to the Wonder World.
At this rate, I'll be dragged into the opponent's Wonder.
Hit the seed with the ball.
Ah, if I go where the spotlight is, I can shoot.
Okay, okay. This isn't particularly a Wonder World yet?
Eh? Don't we have to fill it all up?
I figured it out! What this "Tennis" thing is!
It's a game about the center!
If Wonder Seeds fill up, it's over.
Subaru liked Pinball and Ring Shot.
Or we can remake the room and play normally.
This game is fun, isn't it?
You have the same build, so you fit in Pinball.
Dangerous, I almost got stuck in the Pinball.
Is it dangerous to get close?
It started! Once this starts, I...
Which one, where is the ball!
Seriously, which one is the ball?!
What do we do? Let's remake the room and play normally.
Lastly let's do the one where we get 1000 points.
The one where idiots pass through.
Seriously, this spinning thing... I'm gonna die.
Also the body is huge so coverage is huge.
I know, easy to spot too.
How do you hit a low ball?
I don't know but maybe Y?
Y might be the strongest in this rule.
Y is strong right? It's a Y game.
My ball! My ball! My ball!
Where's the ball, where's the ball, where's the ball.
Subaru-chan, when you started the stream today...
You said "I can only do 1 hour today."
If it's not 1 hour, we'll run out of stamina.
I didn't think it was such an intense game.
No, Mario Tennis for more than an hour is hell.
Because when I played with Nekomata-san before, on N64 or something, the enemy was super strong.
Ah right, we played doubles together.
Yeah, I only remembered that, so I had that feeling. I didn't think it became such a party game.
The amount of information is crazy.
I didn't know it became like this.
It's impossible to do this without making noise.
We have about 10 minutes left anyway.
Then, "Absolutely No Noise Allowed Mario Tennis."
Does that mean there's a punishment game?
I don't really feel like anything is a punishment anymore.
Then, "No Laughing, No Noise Mario Tennis," Start.
Hey, don't make your voice thick.
No, that was pain just now so...
This just becomes a normal serious match.
Wah! A voice is coming to me!
Hey, it's that kind of racket.
I always wonder what Tie Break is.
Does it mean we can do things like Kaidou?
You're getting better! Even battling like idiots!
Laughing really makes you feel alive.
Exactly. If laughter is stolen from us...
We won't know what to do.
Boomerang Snake is crazy! Coming from outside the frame!
Isn't this amazing? 160km/h, isn't that amazing?
Is it time to aim for a Fever Shot?
Wait, I have to guess a 50/50?
Crap, I have too few rackets.
I think this is strong, normally.
Turn it into a grilled banana.
Ah, it appeared, back to Banana.
Crap crap, my field is already...
Nekomata, you should become a tennis player.
No, I can't play tennis because I'm scared of the banana.
I'll charge in assuming the banana doesn't exist.
I see, that might be important actually.
That's right, getting scared of this banana...
Not bad! Since it became a banana it got way stronger.
Maybe you should fear it? The banana.
Let's do one more, one more.
Wait, I'm gonna watch Harry Potter.
Right, if you don't watch Harry Potter you'll die.
Right, you said it'll be close on time.
The Greengrocer is going to see Harry Potter after this.
I'll clean up this banana first!
Look! Who is the guy who set the Greengrocer on fire?!
Greengrocer decides with a Love Smash.
Crap, I'm starting to understand tennis.
But by the time you understand, you're off to Harry Potter.
Returning to the center is important after all.
Crap, Greengrocer is totally on fire.
You can't win just staying back there.
Shut up, if I go forward I burn!
This is the power of the Greengrocer.
Don't know. Something happens. When you take one point from a tie.
Tiger Break. Frieren of the Funeral.
I'll do a Frieren of the Funeral.
Nekomata-san is Frieren of the Funeral...
You're doing Frieren of the Funeral.
Thought about it and went right away.
What happens if you die in Singles?
I can't go easy on you!
Which way, which way, which way... Copy.
No, this isn't the time for that!
Uh oh, dropping a long ball!
Yes, so, everyone, thank you for today as well.
Oi, isn't Pekora playing tennis too?
Wait, was she? Has she finished her slot?
Ranked... Ranked is totally serious though.
Then I'll close up for now.
Thank you for today as well.
A lot of people are coming.
Friday is normal... Friday, Saturday, Sunday are normal.
I'll be streaming, so please come watch.
Everyone, thank you for today too.
